{
  "username": "admin",
  "password": "???"
}

### 1. Pobierz wszystkie zadania
GET {{RestAPI}}/api/zadania
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Accept: application/json

### 2. Pobierz zadanie o id=
GET {{RestAPI}}/api/zadania/3
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Accept: application/json

### 3. Dodaj nowe zadanie 
POST {{RestAPI}}/api/zadania
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "tytul": "Zadanie 3",
  "czyWykonane": false
}

### 4. Usuñ zadanie o id=
DELETE {{RestAPI}}/api/zadania/3
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Accept: application/json

### 5. Zaktualizuj zadanie o id=3
PUT {{RestAPI}}/api/zadania/4
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "id": 4,
  "tytul": "Zadanie 1 - ZROBIONE!",
  "czyWykonane": true
}